      <h1>Library — overview</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        The OPDA Knowledge Base holds roughly 500 MB of source material in
        <code>source/</code> — cloned upstream repos, OPDA's own website mirror,
        meeting packs, video transcripts, third-party reports and external
        references. This section indexes it.
      </p>

      <h2 id="holdings">What's in the archive</h2>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Holding</th><th>Where</th><th>Detail</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Cloned GitHub repos</strong></td>
            <td><a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/03-standards/"><code>source/03-standards/</code></a> + <a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/06-research/smart-data-challenge/code/"><code>source/06-research/smart-data-challenge/code/</code></a> + <a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/07-website/source/"><code>source/07-website/source/</code></a></td>
            <td>5 repos: <code>schemas</code> (3.9 MB), <code>api</code> (38 KB), <code>trust-framework</code> (5.5 MB), <code>web</code> (1.6 MB), <code>smart-data-challenge-2025</code> (1.7 MB). Full git history retained.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>openpropdata.org.uk mirror</strong></td>
            <td><a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/07-website/rendered/"><code>source/07-website/rendered/</code></a></td>
            <td>16 pages + 70 blog posts. Captured 2026-05-13.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>OPDA YouTube channel</strong></td>
            <td><a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/05-engagement/videos-youtube/"><code>source/05-engagement/videos-youtube/</code></a></td>
            <td>15 videos with metadata + transcripts. ~2.5 hours of recordings. <a href="43-video-library.html">Cataloguing page</a>.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>DPMSG Steering Group materials</strong></td>
            <td><a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/04-governance-bodies/steering-group/materials/"><code>source/04-governance-bodies/steering-group/materials/</code></a></td>
            <td>8 meeting packs (Sep 2025 → Apr 2026). <a href="41-meetings-decisions.html">Meeting log</a>.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>DPMSG Working Groups</strong></td>
            <td><a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/04-governance-bodies/working-groups/"><code>source/04-governance-bodies/working-groups/</code></a></td>
            <td>6 working-group folders. Includes the Spring 2025 Interoperability Report. <a href="42-working-groups.html">Group catalog</a>.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Trust Framework PoC documents</strong></td>
            <td><a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/06-research/trust-framework-poc/"><code>source/06-research/trust-framework-poc/</code></a></td>
            <td>Sandbox setup &amp; technical guides, project plan, Raidiam slides, participant kick-off, glossary, cooperation agreement.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Smart Data Challenge entries</strong></td>
            <td><a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/06-research/smart-data-challenge/"><code>source/06-research/smart-data-challenge/</code></a></td>
            <td>Full submission archive incl. prize entries, cost spreadsheets, member-feedback workbooks. <a href="52-smart-data-challenge.html">SDC page</a>.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Third-party reports</strong></td>
            <td><a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/06-research/reports-third-party/"><code>source/06-research/reports-third-party/</code></a></td>
